(1985), Amaral et al. (1987), Barbas & Pandya (1987, 1989), Webster et al. (1993), Hof & Morrison (1995), Carmichael & Price (1994), and Petrides & Pandya (1994). The motor cortex were done according to Matelli et al. (1985) and some recently published and submitted work of Geyer et al. (Geyer et al. 1998a,b; Geyer et al., submitted)."
